results.name: Odd triprimes modulo 10.
link: Reinhard Zumkeller, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000
Index entries for sequences related to final digits of numbers
program: (PARI) do(x)=my(v=List(), t); forprime(p=3, x\9, forprime(q=3, min(x\(3*p), p), t=p*q; forprime(r=3, min(x\t, q), listput(v, t*r)))); Set(v)%10 \\
